{"tid":2178050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全民檢測，141個檢測中心，睇下有冇一間響你屋企左近","createTime":"2020-08-28T06:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T14:33:51.000Z","uid":365791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"34dbb252d4b649119200e29e4faf3355e9af46e8","tid":2178050,"uid":365791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:33:10.000Z","msg":"141檢測中心位置：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.communitytest.gov.hk/locations/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.communitytest.gov.hk%2Flocations%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=66691f6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.communitytest.gov.hk/locations/</a><br />\n<br />\n檢測中心都係學校，社區會堂，同體育館等社區設施，哩d社區設施都係採用中央冷氣，空氣唔流通，又冇負壓設備<br />\n<br />\n而且室內嘅空氣會抽返去室外，哩d檢測中心都係非常接近民居，檢測完病毒會依附響冷氣系統同周圍環境一段長時間，哩d檢測中心隨時成為播毒中心<br />\n<br />\n去唔去都係自願性質，最重要係大家要繼續做好個人防疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98c9de8942a4510349ce5ac9024d4e3bd45913c","tid":2178050,"uid":277054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:34:57.000Z","msg":"啲社區中心勁近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d4fef5e5a8790c75bee42a532a74bb982b2519","tid":2178050,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:36:56.000Z","msg":"屋企隔籬有2個檢測中心做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d771bdf221f1b592f2cd8c57e6572e6bbc0ac0","tid":2178050,"uid":365791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8d4fef5e5a8790c75bee42a532a74bb982b2519","tid":2178050,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T06:36:56.000Z","msg":"屋企隔籬有2個檢測中心做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T07:53:56.000Z","msg":"慘，行遠d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16562dc30caa770801ed96747ce8fa66e570e9e4","tid":2178050,"uid":179825,"like":